### Vision API Quick Tests
### Use REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) — click "Send Request" above each

@base = http://localhost:8765

### Health check
GET {{base}}/api/health

###

### Current models
GET {{base}}/api/models

###

### System metrics
GET {{base}}/api/metrics

###

### Take screenshot
GET {{base}}/screenshot

###

### Execute tool — screenshot
POST {{base}}/api/tool/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "screenshot",
  "parameters": {}
}

###

### Execute tool — read screen (OCR)
POST {{base}}/api/tool/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "read_screen",
  "parameters": {}
}

###

### Execute tool — run command
POST {{base}}/api/tool/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "run_command",
  "parameters": { "command": "echo Vision is alive" }
}

###

### Execute tool — get system info
POST {{base}}/api/tool/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "get_system_info",
  "parameters": {}
}

###

### Switch to DeepSeek (valid key)
POST {{base}}/api/model
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "deepseek",
  "model": "deepseek-chat"
}

###

### Switch to OpenAI GPT-4.1
POST {{base}}/api/model
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4.1"
}

###

### Switch to Ollama
POST {{base}}/api/model
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "ollama",
  "model": "qikfox/ultronv1:latest"
}

###

### Memory — view all
GET {{base}}/api/memory

###

### Memory — add fact
POST {{base}}/api/memory/fact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fact": "User prefers DeepSeek for fast responses when Ollama is slow"
}

###

### ElevenLabs agent — start
POST {{base}}/api/el-agent/start

###

### ElevenLabs agent — stop
POST {{base}}/api/el-agent/stop

###

### Available TTS voices
GET {{base}}/api/voices
